      "message": "[Major] Line 1320: When applying pending editions in handleMessage(), latestEditionId is set to peditIt-\u003esecond.front()-\u003eid before older pending editions are replayed, but the final visible body corresponds to the last pending edition applied. This can tag the next superseded body with the wrong edition id, causing bodyOverwrite injection to associate plugin data with the wrong historical body. Update latestEditionId to the id of the edition that actually produced the current body after all pending editions are processed.\n```suggestion\nauto latestEditionId \u003d peditIt-\u003esecond.front()-\u003eid;\n...\nfor (const auto\u0026 commit : peditIt-\u003esecond) {\n    auto edBody \u003d commit-\u003ebody;\n    edBody[\"id\"] \u003d latestEditionId;\n    sharedCommit-\u003eeditions.emplace_back(std::move(edBody));\n    latestEditionId \u003d commit-\u003eid;\n}\nsharedCommit-\u003elatestEditionId \u003d latestEditionId;\n```",
